    "tag": "section",
    "class": "gps-580626045862937171 gps gpsil",
    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/223a18-2/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=580625973016265224&sectionId=580626045862937171)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggPLaqS7duJ_text","label":"ggPLaqS7duJ_text","default":"How to Get the Best Results from Your Nifora Bio-Collagen Mask"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbRr_BVjbY_text","label":"ggbRr_BVjbY_text","default":"<p>Watch this quick tutorial and see how simple it is to use your mask for maximum benefits.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4M3qQLhLp_text","label":"gg4M3qQLhLp_text","default":"<p>Step 1: Start with a clean skin</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg1KWrL-WzD_text","label":"gg1KWrL-WzD_text","default":"<p>Your mask works best on clean, dry skin. Gently cleanse and pat dry to create the perfect base. This allows the collagen and hyaluronic acid to penetrate deeply without any barriers.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZ0Jfhswrd_text","label":"ggZ0Jfhswrd_text","default":"<p>Step 2: Apply &amp; Adhere</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4radNKjqp_text","label":"gg4radNKjqp_text","default":"<p>Your mask comes in two pieces for a perfect fit. Apply the bottom half first, then the top. The hydrogel material will cling like a second skin, ensuring every contour gets the full treatment. No slipping or sliding!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbHY6H5rRw_text","label":"ggbHY6H5rRw_text","default":"<p>Step 3: Relax &amp; Transform (2+ Hours)</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggujmk9aoOB_text","label":"ggujmk9aoOB_text","default":"<p>This is where the magic happens. Let the mask work for at least 2-3 hours. As it turns from white to clear, you know the 34ml of potent serum is being fully absorbed into your skin. Many users even sleep in it for maximum hydration.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggO_pM7qsV6_text","label":"ggO_pM7qsV6_text","default":"<p>Step 4: Reveal Your Glow</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggj5FivgyIt_text","label":"ggj5FivgyIt_text","default":"<p>Once the mask is transparent, gently peel it off. No need to rinse! Simply pat any remaining essence into your skin, neck, and décolletage for a dewy, hydrated finish that lasts.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggVBw2jAe3a_text","label":"ggVBw2jAe3a_text","default":"Did you know your skin can benefit from different masks?"},{"type":"html","id":"gg-cjAYongE_text","label":"gg-cjAYongE_text","default":"<p>Your skin has more than one need — that’s why we created a collection of masks for hydration, firming, anti-wrinkle, and radiance. Many of our customers mix and match masks throughout the week for complete care.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggky3RauH0H_text","label":"ggky3RauH0H_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(48,48,48);font-size:15px;\">✔️ </span>Your Go-To for Smoother Skin</p><p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(48,48,48);font-size:15px;\">✔️ </span>Targets visible signs of aging and deep-set wrinkles.</p><p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(48,48,48);font-size:15px;\">✔️</span> Restores firmness and elasticity for a youthful look.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg8bTxKYeih_label","label":"gg8bTxKYeih_label","default":"Add to cart"},{"type":"html","id":"gg8bTxKYeih_outOfStockLabel","label":"gg8bTxKYeih_outOfStockLabel","default":"Out of stock"},{"type":"html","id":"gg8bTxKYeih_unavailableLabel","label":"gg8bTxKYeih_unavailableLabel","default":"Unavailable"},{"type":"html","id":"gg8bTxKYeih_variantSelectionRequiredMessage","label":"gg8bTxKYeih_variantSelectionRequiredMessage","default":"Please select a variant to add product to cart"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4mlVraqjq_text","label":"gg4mlVraqjq_text","default":"<p>✔️ For a Bright, Even-Toned Glow</p><p>✔️ Fades the appearance of dark spots and hyperpigmentation.</p><p>✔️ Brightens dullness for a luminous, even-toned complexion.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggXkV07OJTr_label","label":"ggXkV07OJTr_label","default":"Add to cart"},{"type":"html","id":"ggXkV07OJTr_outOfStockLabel","label":"ggXkV07OJTr_outOfStockLabel","default":"Out of stock"},{"type":"html","id":"ggXkV07OJTr_unavailableLabel","label":"ggXkV07OJTr_unavailableLabel","default":"Unavailable"},{"type":"html","id":"ggXkV07OJTr_variantSelectionRequiredMessage","label":"ggXkV07OJTr_variantSelectionRequiredMessage","default":"Please select a variant to add product to cart"},{"type":"html","id":"ggv1xQ6w1EB_text","label":"ggv1xQ6w1EB_text","default":"<p>✔️ The Ultimate Skin Reset</p><p>✔️ Calms sensitivity and reduces the look of redness overnight.</p><p>✔️ Repairs and strengthens a compromised skin barrier.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggixwyPS9lk_label","label":"ggixwyPS9lk_label","default":"Add to cart"},{"type":"html","id":"ggixwyPS9lk_outOfStockLabel","label":"ggixwyPS9lk_outOfStockLabel","default":"Out of stock"},{"type":"html","id":"ggixwyPS9lk_unavailableLabel","label":"ggixwyPS9lk_unavailableLabel","default":"Unavailable"},{"type":"html","id":"ggixwyPS9lk_variantSelectionRequiredMessage","label":"ggixwyPS9lk_variantSelectionRequiredMessage","default":"Please select a variant to add product to cart"},{"type":"html","id":"ggo74Z5lcs1_text","label":"ggo74Z5lcs1_text","default":"<p>✔️ For Intensive Hydration &amp; Repair</p><p>✔️ Deeply hydrates and promotes skin cell regeneration.</p><p>✔️ Revitalizes tired, damaged skin for a plumper look.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggFideGc6fN_label","label":"ggFideGc6fN_label","default":"Add to cart"},{"type":"html","id":"ggFideGc6fN_outOfStockLabel","label":"ggFideGc6fN_outOfStockLabel","default":"Out of stock"},{"type":"html","id":"ggFideGc6fN_unavailableLabel","label":"ggFideGc6fN_unavailableLabel","default":"Unavailable"},{"